  ('medical-tech-moex-08948', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-105-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於紙錠擴散法藥敏試驗之結果判讀，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["貼上紙錠之培養皿，一般在35℃培養16至18小時後即可觀察", "抑制圈的直徑需以尺或測徑器（caliper）測量", "同一抗生素對不同之細菌會有不同之判讀標準", "若抑制圈內僅有一些零星大的菌落出現，可以忽略"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b21f6367bb7f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6c5d5eeabde3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105020", "c": "308", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次醫師牙醫師藥師分階段、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 53, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-08949', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-105-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於chloramphenicol之敘述，何者正確？', '["與細菌30S核糖體次單元結合，抑制胜肽的延長", "與合成細胞壁的酵素結合，造成細胞壁合成功能受損", "抑菌範圍很廣泛，但因為具有毒性目前很少使用", "是屬於殺菌（bactericidal）性質的抗生素"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b21f6367bb7f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6c5d5eeabde3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105020", "c": "308", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次醫師牙醫師藥師分階段、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 54, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-08950', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-105-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於Azole類抗黴菌藥物之敘述，那些正確？①Imidazoles與Triazoles屬此類  ②屬於廣', '["僅①②", "僅②③", "僅①③", "①②③"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b21f6367bb7f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6c5d5eeabde3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105020", "c": "308", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次醫師牙醫師藥師分階段、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 55, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-08951', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-105-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '通常肺結核病人open pulmonary cavity內之抗藥肺結核菌數目會比closed caseous lesion內 的數目為：', '["多", "少", "一樣", "不能比較"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b21f6367bb7f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6c5d5eeabde3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105020", "c": "308", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次醫師牙醫師藥師分階段、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 56, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-08952', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-105-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於發生院內感染進行細菌分型的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["利用抗生素敏感性分型，將兩株細菌分為不同型，若用基因分型分析也必能區別為不同型", "細菌的基因分型（genotyping）是以萃取細菌的mRNA來進行分析", "若持續一年在不同的住院病人身上分離出同種細菌，並以脈衝式電泳分析為同一型，則可 判定為群突發菌（outbreak strains）", "多重位點基因序列分型（Multilocus Sequence Typing）也常用於細菌基因分型 （genotyping）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b21f6367bb7f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6c5d5eeabde3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105020", "c": "308", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次醫師牙醫師藥師分階段、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 57, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-08953', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-105-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關肺結核桿菌直接及間接法藥敏試驗之比較，下列敘述何者正確？', '["間接法較易污染", "兩法均皆需培養出細菌，以製備接種液", "直接法易產生突變株", "間接法較易標準化"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b21f6367bb7f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6c5d5eeabde3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105020", "c": "308", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次醫師牙醫師藥師分階段、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 58, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-08954', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-105-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種藥物適合治療位於巨嗜細胞內之肺結核菌？', '["Streptomycin", "Pyrazinamide", "Amphotericin B", "Nystatin"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b21f6367bb7f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6c5d5eeabde3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105020", "c": "308", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次醫師牙醫師藥師分階段、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 59, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-08955', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-105-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Clinical and Laboratory Standards Institute（CLSI）所定的黴菌藥敏試驗法（M27-A），適 用於下列何菌？', '["Aspergillus flavus", "Sporothrix schenckii", "Cryptococcus neoformans", "Rhizopus arrhizus"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b21f6367bb7f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6c5d5eeabde3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105020", "c": "308", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次醫師牙醫師藥師分階段、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 60, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-08956', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-105-bccd9a5a', 'sub-medical-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '會產生類似Cholera toxin之對熱不穩定毒素（heat-labile toxin）之Escherichia coli，是屬於 下列何型？', '["Enteropathogenic E. coli（EPEC）", "Enterohemorrhagic E. coli（EHEC）", "Enterotoxigenic E. coli（ETEC）", "Enteroinvasive E. coli（EIEC）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b21f6367bb7f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6c5d5eeabde3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105020", "c": "308", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學與臨床微生物學（包括細菌與黴菌）", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次醫師牙醫師藥師分階段、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 61, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
